name: MODE
description: The mode in which the application is running.

name: VERCEL_ENV
description: The Vercel environment. This variable is set by Vercel when the application is running in a Vercel environment.

name: NODE_ENV
description: The environment the application is running in. This variable is a duplicate of `ENVIRONMENT` to support use in external packages.

name: TEST
description: An indicator that specifies the current runtime is a test environment.

name: MINIMAL
description: An indicator that specifies the current runtime is a minimal environment.

name: WT_SESSION
description: The terminal emulator session ID. This variable is set by certain terminal emulators.

name: TERMINUS_SUBLIME
description: An indicator that specifies the current terminal is running Terminus Sublime. This variable is set by certain terminal emulators.

name: ConEmuTask
description: The ConEmu task name. This variable is set by certain terminal emulators.

name: TERMINAL_EMULATOR
description: The terminal emulator name. This variable is set by certain terminal emulators.

name: NO_COLOR
description: An indicator that specifies the current runtime is a no color environment.

name: FORCE_COLOR
description: An indicator that specifies the current runtime is a force color environment.

name: STORM_DATA_DIR
description: The Storm Stack application's runtime data directory.

name: STORM_CONFIG_DIR
description: The Storm Stack application's configuration data directory.

name: STORM_CACHE_DIR
description: The Storm Stack application's cached data directory.

name: STORM_LOG_DIR
description: The Storm Stack application's logging directory.

name: STORM_TEMP_DIR
description: The Storm Stack application's temporary data directory.

name: LOCALAPPDATA
description: A variable that specifies the current user's local application data directory on Windows.

name: APPDATA
description: A variable that specifies the application data directory on Windows.

name: XDG_DATA_HOME
description: A variable that specifies the data path in the home directory on Linux systems using the XDG base directory specification.

name: XDG_CONFIG_HOME
description: A variable that specifies the configuration path in the home directory on Linux systems using the XDG base directory specification.

name: XDG_CACHE_HOME
description: A variable that specifies the cache path in the home directory on Linux systems using the XDG base directory specification.

name: XDG_STATE_HOME
description: A variable that specifies the state directory on Linux systems using the XDG base directory specification.

name: DEVENV_RUNTIME
description: A variable that specifies the [Devenv](https://devenv.sh/) runtime directory.

name: XDG_RUNTIME_DIR
description: A variable that specifies the runtime directory on Linux systems using the XDG base directory specification.

name: BUILD_ID
description: The unique identifier for the build.

name: BUILD_TIMESTAMP
description: The timestamp the build was ran at.

name: RELEASE_ID
description: The unique identifier for the release.

name: PLATFORM
description: The platform for which the application was built.

name: ERROR_URL
description: An API end point to lookup error messages given an error code.

name: INCLUDE_ERROR_DATA
description: Indicates if error data should be included.

name: STORM_STACK_LOCAL
description: An indicator that specifies the application is running in the local Storm Stack development environment.

name: APP_NAME
description: The name of the application.

name: BUILD_CHECKSUM
description: A checksum hash created during the build.

name: ORGANIZATION
description: The name of the organization that maintains the application.

name: DEFAULT_TIMEZONE
description: The default timezone for the application.

name: DEFAULT_LOCALE
description: The default locale for the application.

name: LOG_LEVEL
description: The default lowest log level to accept. If `null`, the logger will reject all records. This value only applies if `lowestLogLevel` is not provided to the `logs` configuration.

name: HELP
description: Show help information.

name: VERSION
description: Show the version of the application.

name: NO_BANNER
description: Hide the banner displayed while running the CLI application (will be set to true if running in a CI pipeline).

name: NO_INTERACTIVE
description: Disable interactive mode (will be set to true if running in a CI pipeline).

name: NAME
description: The name of the variable to set in the variables store

name: VALUE
description: The value to set for the variable

name: HOST
description: The host to bind the server to

name: PORT
description: The port to bind the server to

name: COMPRESS
description: Should the server serve compressed files?

name: NO_COMPRESS
description: The inverse of the compress option.

name: LOAD_ENV
description: Should the server load environment variables from the .env file?

name: NO_LOAD_ENV
description: The inverse of the load-env option.

name: FILE
description: The file to add to the file system

name: TYPE
description: The type of the file

name: FORCE_HYPERLINK
description: An indicator that specifies the current runtime should force hyperlinks in terminal output.

name: NETLIFY
description: The netlify build ID. This value is set by certain CI/CD systems.

name: TEAMCITY_VERSION
description: The teamcity version. This value is set by certain CI/CD systems.

name: TERM_PROGRAM
description: The terminal program name. This variable is set by certain terminal emulators.

name: TERM_PROGRAM_VERSION
description: The terminal program version. This variable is set by certain terminal emulators.

name: CURSOR_TRACE_ID
description: The cursor trace ID. This variable is set by certain terminal emulators.

name: VTE_VERSION
description: The VTE version. This variable is set by certain terminal emulators.

name: TERM
description: The terminal type. This variable is set by certain CI/CD systems.

name: APP_VERSION
description: The version of the application.

name: VERBOSE
description: Enable verbose output.

name: INTERACTIVE
description: Enable interactive mode (will be set to false if running in a CI pipeline).

name: SENTRY_DSN
description: The DSN for Sentry

name: ENVIRONMENT
description: The environment the application is running in. This value will be populated with the value of `MODE` if not provided.

name: RELEASE_TAG
description: The tag for the release. This is generally in the format of "\<APP_NAME\>\@\<APP_VERSION\>".

name: DEBUG
description: Indicates if the application is running in debug mode.

name: STACKTRACE
description: Indicates if error stack traces should be captured.
